sfBBCodeParserPlugin
--------------------

The **sfBBCodeParserPlugin** ... 

Installation
============

 * Install the plugin

        $ symfony plugin:install sfBBCodeParserPlugin

   (or download it and unzip in your /plugins directory)

 * Clear you cache

        $ symfony cc

Configuration
=============


Usage
=====

    [php]

Demo
====

If you want to run the tests, enable the `sfBBCodeParser` module in your `settings.yml`
file, then call `sfBBCodeParser7`. (If you have desactivated the default symfony routes, 
a `routing.yml` file is included in the `config` folder of the plugin. 
   
